<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml">
<head>
    <title>CSS Test: visibility hidden still occupies space</title>
    <link rel="match" href="visibility-hidden-001-ref.xht" />
    <style type="text/css">
        div.a {
            width: 100px;
            height: 50px;
            background-color: green;
        }
        div.b {
            visibility: hidden;
            width: 100px;
            height: 50px;
            background-color: red;
        }
        div.c {
            width: 100px;
            height: 50px;
            background-color: green;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <p>Test passes if there are two green rectangles with a gap between them and no red.</p>
    <div class="a"></div>
    <div class="b"></div>
    <div class="c"></div>
</body>
</html>